This is the wrapper framework laid out to start building Spring based Web apps with Hibernate ORM layer and Spring MVC
in scala programming language. The purpose of this project is to get you started quickly in Scala web app development 
over a tried and tested java framework: Spring.

This project provides sample hibernate entities, models, DAOs, Service and Controller classes. There are also
many framework level classes to help handle exceptions and errors in the project you may start developing using this.


Used components:
Spring 3+
Hibernate 3+
Scala 2.9+
Maven


